"at night|\n"
"|<notr>Bunya</notr>|Ring-tail possum|Top star in Southern Cross|\n"
"|<notr>Chargee Gnowee</notr>|Elder sister, sister of the sun|Venus|\n"
"|<notr>Bittur</notr>|Larvae of the woodant|&mdash;|\n"
